Amoxicillin is used in combination with [vonoprazan] and [clarithromycin] as co-packaged triple therapy or in combination with [vonoprazan] as co-packaged dual therapy to treat _H. pylori_ infection in adults.[L41695]', '', '', 712, '2022-07-25', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
